org.ietf.nea.pa.attribute.util

Interface PaAttributeValueErrorInformationUnsupportedAttributeBuilder

  • All Superinterfaces:
    PaAttributeSubValueBuilder<PaAttributeValueErrorInformationUnsupportedAttribute>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    PaAttributeValueErrorInformationUnsupportedAttributeBuilderIetf

    public interface PaAttributeValueErrorInformationUnsupportedAttributeBuilder
extends PaAttributeSubValueBuilder<PaAttributeValueErrorInformationUnsupportedAttribute>
    Generic builder to build an integrity measurement unsupported attribute error information value compliant to RFC 5792. It can be used in a fluent way.
